ras/chaos.gif?t=1706056220\" /><br><br><br><u><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Expand, Fortify, and Dominate</h2></strong></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Grow your base and deploy an array of towers. Harness the power of your personal drone for strategic advantage and secure victory over your enemies.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316530/extras/build.gif?t=1706056220\" /><br><br><u><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customization at Your Fingertips</h2></strong></u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Design and personalize your enemies. Upload images to decide who you'll be fighting against.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>It's not just tower defense, it's Buster's world, and it's waiting for you to conquer it. Your strategy, your victories. Welcome to the next-gen of tower defense\u2014where you don't just play the game, you shape it.</strong></h2>","developers":["Otis Anderson"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1316530/header.jpg?t=1706056220","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"This game is post-release. Most games originally release as Alpha or Beta and promise improvements over time. This game will be released post-released, meaning it will become more SCUFFED over time.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256995958,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256995958/movie480.mp4?t=1706036318","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256995958/movie_max.mp4?t=1706036318"},"name"